INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('978-12-34567-89-7', 'Clap When You Land', '34.50','Camino Rios lives for the summers when her father visits her in the Dominican Republic. But this time, on the day when his plane is supposed to land, Camino arrives at the airport to see crowds of crying people.', '2020-03-12', '300', 'Comedy', 'Elizabeth Acevedo', 'P0001');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('978-03-23456-16-0', 'A Good Girl Guide to Murder', '38.50','Pretty and popular high school senior Andie Bell was murdered by her boyfriend, Sal Singh, who then killed himself. It was all anyone could talk about. And five years later, Pip sees how the tragedy still haunts her town.', '2020-03-18', '350', 'Thriller', 'Holly Jackson', 'P0005');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('965-19-45632-99-0', 'One Of Us Is Next', '40.00','A ton of copycat gossip apps have popped up since Simon died, but in the year since the Bayview four were cleared of his shocking death, no one has been able to fill the gossip void quite like he could. The problem is no one has the facts.', '2020-04-01', '400', 'Horror', 'Karen M. Magnus', 'P0015');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('944-01-36667-66-3', 'Felix Ever After', '32.60','Felix Love has never been in love—and, yes, he’s painfully aware of the irony. He desperately wants to know what it’s like and why it seems so easy for everyone but him to find someone.', '2020-04-16', '440', 'Romance', 'Kacen Clendder', 'P0008');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('925-12-12352-03-5', 'You Should See Me In A Crown', '25.00','Liz Lighty has always believed she is too black, too poor, too awkward to shine in her small, rich, prom-obsessed midwestern town. But it is okay -- Liz has a plan that will get her out of Campbell, Indiana, forever: attend the uber.', '2020-04-28', '120', 'RomCom', 'Leah Johnson', 'P0011');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('922-24-29837-05-2', 'The Inheritance Game', '50.00','Avery Grambs has a plan for a better future: survive high school, win a scholarship, and get out. But her fortunes change in an instant when billionaire Tobias Hawthorne dies and leaves Avery virtually his entire fortune. The catch?', '2020-05-11', '500', 'Fantasy', 'Jennifer Lyn Barns', 'P0004');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('912-00-98283-43-6', 'The Hand On The Wall', '51.00','Ellingham Academy must be cursed. Three people are now dead. One, a victim of either a prank gone wrong or a murder. Another, dead by misadventure. And now, an accident in Burlington has claimed another life.', '2020-05-15', '150', 'Fantasy', 'Maureen Johnson', 'P0010');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('909-87-09485-33-1', 'Majesty', '15.40','Power is intoxicating. Like first love, it can leave you breathless. Princess Beatrice was born with it. Princess Samantha was born with less. Some, like Nina Gonzalez, are pulled into it. Ahem, we are looking at you Daphne Deighton.', '2020-05-29', '111', 'Comedy', 'Katherine McGee', 'P0005');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('910-90-03492-22-6', 'Tweet Cute', '20.00','All’s fair in love and cheese ― that is, until Pepper and Jack’s spat turns into a viral Twitter war. Little do they know, while they’re publicly duking it out with snarky memes and retweet battles.', '2020-06-18', '120', 'RomCom', 'Emma Lord', 'P0013');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('922-69-83927-11-3', 'I Feel Bad About My Neck', '67.00','With her disarming, intimate, voice, and dry sense of humor, Nora Ephron shares with us her ups and downs in I Feel Bad About My Neck, a candid look at women who are dealing with the tribulations of maintenance, menopause and life itself.', '2006-08-20', '43', 'Self-Enrichment', 'Nora Ephron', 'P0015');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('872-35-00928-00-9', 'Broken Glass', '44.44','Alain Mabanckou’s riotous new novel centers on the patrons of a run-down bar in the Congo. In a country that appears to have forgotten the importance of remembering, a bar regular, Broken Glass has been elected to record their stories for posterity.', '2005-01-11', '120', 'Cultural', 'Alain Mabanckou', 'P0004');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('832-56-09478-33-8', 'A Little Life', '77.00',' Yet their greatest challenge, each comes to realize, is Jude himself, by midlife a terrifyingly talented litigator yet an increasingly broken man, and haunted by what he fears is a degree of trauma.', '2015-12-01', '100', 'Comtemporary', 'Hanya Yanighara', 'P0002');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('809-12-89238-22-0', 'Coraline', '21.12','In Coraline family new flat are twenty-one windows and fourteen doors. The fourteenth is locked, and on the other side is only a brick wall, until the day Coraline unlocks the door to find a passage to another flat in another house just like her own.', '2002-01-22', '220', 'Horror', 'Nail Gailman', 'P0012');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('781-10-98237-23-6', 'Seven Brief Lessons on Physics', '89.00','Carlo Rovelli offers surprising—and surprisingly easy to grasp—explanations of general relativity, quantum mechanics, elementary particles, gravity, black holes, the complex architecture of the universe, and the role humans play in this world.', '2014-10-09', '600', 'Science', 'Carlo Rovelli', 'P0007');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('755-52-09812-08-8', 'Underland', '90.00','Traveling through the dizzying expanse of geologic time—from prehistoric art in Norwegian sea caves, to the blue depths of the Greenland ice cap, to a deep-sunk "hiding place" where nuclear waste will be stored for 100,000 years to come.', '2010-05-24', '99', 'History', 'Robert Macfarlane', 'P0001');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('710-49-89487-90-2', 'Shadow Witch', '11.50','Okay, so I’m in trouble. Big trouble. I’m broke. Worse, my boyfriend of five years just dumped me. What do I do? I move in with my three eccentric aunts in their family home. Sounds exciting, only this massive farmhouse likes to eat men.', '2018-02-22', '342', 'Fantasy', 'Kim Richardson', 'P0005');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('700-65-09322-42-4', 'Beach Read', '10.00','Augustus Everett is an acclaimed author of literary fiction. January Andrews writes bestselling romance. When she pens a happily ever after, he kills off his entire cast. They are polar opposites.', '2017-03-22', '376', 'Romance', 'Emily Harry', 'P0006');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('700-12-43654-12-2', 'The Switch', '39.10','When overachiever Leena Cotton is ordered to take a two-month sabbatical after blowing a big presentation at work, she escapes to her grandmother Eileen house for some overdue rest. Eileen is newly single and about to turn eighty.', '2017-03-22', '211', 'Romance', 'Bryn Brairs', 'P0006');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('689-15-22345-00-1', 'The Midnight Library', '34.50','Between life and death there is a library, and within that library, the shelves go on forever. Every book provides a chance to try another life you could have lived.', '2020-03-21', '111', 'Fantasy', 'Elizabeth Acevedo', 'P0012');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('678-11-32222-89-7', 'The Guest List', '31.50','But perfection is for plans, and people are all too human. It is not long after the cake is cut and the champagne popped that resentments. Worse yet, the latest barometer reading shows the weather has shifted from FAIR to CHANGEABLE.', '2020-03-12', '324', 'Mystery', 'Elizabeth Acevedo', 'P0012');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('978-43-34367-83-2', 'The Vanishing Half', '23.90','The Vignes twin sisters will always be identical. But after growing up together in a small, southern black community and running away at age sixteen, it not just the shape of their daily lives that is different as adults.', '2003-03-12', '100', 'History', 'Brit Bennet', 'P0001');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('342-12-34567-89-7', 'House of Earth and Blood', '78.90','Bryce Quinlan had the perfect life—working hard all day and partying all night—until a demon murdered her closest friends, leaving her bereft, wounded, and alone. When the accused is behind bars, Bryce finds herself at the heart of the investigation.', '2021-04-12', '600', 'Fantasy', 'Sarah J. Maas', 'P0003');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('425-12-34567-43-8', 'Strange Planet', '9.00','Straight from the mind of New York Times bestselling author Nathan W. Pyle comes an adorable and profound universe. Based on the phenomenally popular Instagram of the same name, Strange Planet covers a full life cycle of the planet’s inhabitants.', '2021-01-12', '700', 'Comedy', 'Nathan W. Pyle', 'P0011');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('999-12-34567-22-1', 'A Promised Land', '99.99','In the stirring, highly anticipated first volume of his presidential memoirs, Barack Obama tells the story of his odyssey from young man searching for his identity to leader, describing in strikingly personal detail both his political education.', '2020-12-12', '300', 'Biography', 'Barack Obama', 'P0015');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('999-99-67456-89-7', 'Caste: The Origins of Our Discontents', '88.88','In this brilliant book, Isabel Wilkerson gives us a masterful portrait of an unseen phenomenon in America as she explores, through an immersive, deeply researched narrative and stories about real people, .', '2020-12-12', '780', 'Politics', 'Isabel Wickerson', 'P0014');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('456-12-34567-89-9', 'Heartstopper: Volume Three', '34.50','Charlie didnt think Nick could ever like him back, but now they are officially boyfriends. Nicks even found the courage to come out to his mum.', '2020-12-12', '99', 'RomCom', 'Alice Olseman', 'P0009');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('978-12-21111-82-1', 'Such a Fun Age', '22.22','Alix Chamberlain is a woman who gets what she wants and has made a living, with her confidence-driven brand, showing other women how to do the same. Emira Tucker, is confronted while watching the Chamberlains toddler one night', '2019-08-12', '100', 'RomCom', 'Alice Olseman', 'P0009');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('334-00-34567-89-7', 'Dearly', '34.50','In Dearly, Margaret Atwood’s first collection of poetry in over a decade, Atwood addresses themes such as love, loss, the passage of time, the nature of nature and - zombies. ', '2012-08-12', '50', 'Poetry', 'Carla Rainbow', 'P0003');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('334-12-34567-65-2', 'From Blood and Ash', '50.50','Chosen from birth to usher in a new era, Poppy’s life has never been her own. The life of the Maiden is solitary. Never to be touched. Never to be looked upon. Never to be spoken to. Never to experience pleasure.', '2011-08-12', '900', 'Romance', 'Jennifer L. Armentrout', 'P0009');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('121-12-22367-49-7', 'To Sleep in a Sea of Stars', '94.50','Kira Navárez dreamed of life on new worlds. Now shes awakened a nightmare. During a routine survey mission on an uncolonized planet, Kira finds an alien relic.', '2021-01-01', '234', 'Thriller', 'Jennifer Ashton', 'P0010');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('988-23-33567-89-4', 'Mexican Gothic', '34.00','After receiving a frantic letter from her newly-wed cousin begging for someone to save her from a mysterious doom, Noemí Taboada heads to High Place, a distant house in the Mexican countryside.', '2013-02-01', '33', 'Horror', 'Elizabeth Garton', 'P0015');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('333-01-34344-22-7', 'That Summer', '8.90','Daisy Shoemaker can’t sleep. With a thriving cooking business, full schedule of volunteer work, and a beautiful home in the Philadelphia suburbs, she should be content. But her teenage daughter can be a handful; her husband can be distant.', '2021-05-01', '233', 'Romance', 'Katie Garton', 'P0007');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('915-12-33217-84-1', 'The Atmospherians', '12.00','Sasha Marcus was once the epitome of contemporary success: an internet sensation, social media darling, and a creator of a high profile wellness brand for women. But a confrontation with an abusive troll has taken a horrifying turn.', '2021-06-01', '556', 'Contemporary', 'Leon Ling', 'P0004');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('112-11-12312-23-7', 'The Premonition: A Pandemic Story', '40.90','Fortunately, we are still a nation of skeptics. Fortunately, there are those among us who study pandemics and are willing to look unflinchingly at worst-case scenarios. ', '2021-04-11', '500', 'Contemporary', 'Matthow Tan', 'P0008');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('978-12-34567-89-4', 'Youre Invited', '34.50','The most universal strategy for success is creating meaningful connections with those who can impact you, your life.', '2021-04-11', '223', 'Contemporary', 'Matthow Tan', 'P0008');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('978-12-34567-39-2', 'Lets Talk About Hard Things', '70.00','Anna Sale wants you to have that conversation. You know the one. The one that you’ve been avoiding or putting off, maybe for years.', '2021-04-11', '223', 'Romance', 'Melissa Mel', 'P0011');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('978-12-34333-90-2', 'The Ones Were Meant to Find', '60.60','Cee has been trapped on an abandoned island for three years without any recollection of how she arrived, or memories from her life prior.','2013-04-23', '211', 'Sci-Fi', 'Ciber Cheng', 'P0012');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('900-12-34567-89-7', 'China: The Novel', '77.77','Edward Rutherfurd has enthralled millions of readers with his grand, sweeping historical sagas. That tell the history of a famous place over multiple generations.', '2003-11-23', '23', 'History', 'Au Yang Ming Cheng', 'P0013');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('900-10-30007-00-0', 'The Plot', '32.50','Jacob Finch Bonner was once a promising young novelist with a respectably published first book. Today, hes teaching in a third-rate MFA program and struggling to maintain whats left of his self-respect.', '2007-01-02', '50', 'Mystery', 'Ling Ling', 'P0003');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('100-12-34567-10-2', 'Local Woman Missing', '10.50','Shelby Tebow is the first to go missing. Not long after, Meredith Dickey and her six-year-old daughter, Delilah, vanish just blocks away from where Shelby was last seen, striking fear into their once-peaceful community.', '2001-11-23', '10', 'Thriller', 'Josh Cheng', 'P0015');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('500-33-33567-89-7', 'Project Hail Mary', '24.50','Ryland Grace is the sole survivor on a desperate, last-chance mission--and if he fails, humanity and the earth itself will perish.','2005-12-22', '188', 'Thriller', 'Josh Cheng', 'P0015');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('200-12-00001-29-7', 'We Are Satellites', '34.50','Val and Julie just want whats best for their kids, David and Sophie. So when teenage son David comes home one day asking for a Pilot, a new brain implant to help with school.', '2011-02-22', '100', 'Sci-Fi', 'Amelia Hart', 'P0012');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('380-12-11211-12-2', 'Incredible Doom', '12.50','Allison is drowning under the weight of her manipulative stage magician father. When he brings home the family’s first computer, she escapes into a thrilling new world.', '2020-12-22', '900', 'Sci-Fi', 'Coco Iywa', 'P0009');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('666-65-37867-89-7', 'Turtle in Paradise', '92.00','Life isnt like the movies. But then again, 11-year-old Turtle is no Shirley Temple. Shes smart and tough and has seen enough of the world not to expect a Hollywood ending', '2010-02-02', '409', 'Fantasy', 'Coco Iywa', 'P0009');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('201-12-12382-32-7', 'Wynd', '10.00','Wynd seems like a regular boy in the fantastical world of Esseriel, except he’s got a magical secret. Now he’s set off on a journey with his best friend and the boy of his dreams.', '2014-12-23', '922', 'Horror', 'Ishli Ioko', 'P0014');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('890-92-34567-89-7', 'Mary Jane', '99.99','In 1970s Baltimore, fourteen-year-old Mary Jane loves cooking with her mother, singing in her church choir, and enjoying her family’s subscription to the Broadway Show Tunes of the Month record club. ', '2021-09-09', '112', 'Contemporary', 'Julian Mars', 'P0004');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('550-55-55554-54-4', 'Ariadne', '20.50','As Princesses of Crete and daughters of the fearsome King Minos, Ariadne and her sister Phaedra grow up hearing the hoofbeats and bellows of the Minotaur echo from the Labyrinth beneath the palace.', '2021-12-30', '500', 'Fantasy', 'Julian Mars', 'P0006');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('223-12-12423-66-7', 'Firebreak', '5.50','Like everyone else she knows,Mallory is an orphan of the corporate war. As a child, she lost her parents, her home, and her entire building in an airstrike. ', '2004-09-11', '80', 'Sci-Fi', 'Clara Clam', 'P0010');
INSERT INTO Book VALUES ('115-12-34567-89-5', 'Hang the Moon', '60.60','Brendon Lowell loves love. It’s why he created a dating app to help people find their one true pairing and why he’s convinced “the one” is out there, even if he hasn’t met her yet. Or... has he?', '2009-10-11', '55', 'Romance', 'Heartz Lim', 'P0003');
